name: Scale Resin Necklace - Mustard
description:
Scale necklace is handmade from resin and beautifully finished to a soft matte feel. This necklace is inspired by the flickering scales on a fish. 

Materials: Resin, waxed cotton cord and clasp (lead & nickel free)
Making: Moulded from coloured resin, then sanded and polished to a soft matte finish. Strung together on wax coated cotton cord.
Size: Drop length approx 27cm

Making: Moulded from coloured resin, then sanded and polished to a soft matte finish. Strung together on wax coated cotton cord.

name: Pebble Necklace - Resin/Bamboo - Green
description:
Pebble Necklace is beautifully finished to a soft matte feel. It is hand crafted from resin with inlays of bamboo. Wear it long over an outfit or at a shorter length sitting directly on your body. 

Materials: Resin with inlayed bamboo
Making: Individual beads are moulded from coloured resin, then sanded and polished to a soft matte finish. Two of the beads are moulded with bamboo to create a natural finish. The beads are strung together on wax coated cotton cord.
Size: Drop length approx 60cm

name: Resin Stacking Rings NEW COLOURS!
description:
These rings are handmade from resin. Each piece is moulded and hand finished to create a smooth matte surface. 

- Overall size: 22 x 30mm
- Ring size: One size only (approx '18' in ring sizing). 
- Rings are sold separately but can also be worn as a set of 2 or 3.

FREE! postage to Australia and New Zealand.

name: Small Resin Studs
description:
The Small Round Stud are handmade from resin and are set on hypoallergenic surgical steel posts. These studs are the perfect size to wear all day and all night. Coming in 6 colours you will have a pair to match every outfit. 

- Size of resin disk: Diameter is 10mm x 3mm
- Making: Each resin disk is moulded and hand finished to create a smooth matte surface. The resin is then attached to surgical steel earring posts.

*Note: Studs are sold as an individual pair.

name: Rockpool Resin Necklace - Black/Bamboo
description:
Rockpool Necklace is inspired by rocky outlets where pools of water create the small ecosystems of the sea. Each bead is handmade from resin and bamboo and is then sanded and finished to a soft matte feel. Wear it long over an outfit or at a shorter length sitting directly on your body. 

Materials: Resin with inlayed bamboo
Making: Individual beads are moulded from coloured resin with bamboo inlays to create a nature finish, they are then sanded and polished to a soft matte finish. The beads are strung together on wax coated cotton cord.
Size: Drop length approx 60cm
